              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Fiery Avenger</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>First hail Inte -- then as a precaution to make sure you can finish the quest...hand in your Ghoulbane first (easiest to get back if you lose it). If he accepts it, hand in Soulfire, the Head of Miragul and the Robe of Miragul to Inte to receive the Fiery Avenger.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 rowspan=10><b>Mark of Atonement</b></td>

                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Tainted Darksteel Breastplate</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Kill Scorn Banshees in the Plane of Hate. When one is killed, a Thought Corruptor will spawn.  You must kill it.</td>
              </tr>

              <tr>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=150 align=left>Pure Crystal</td>
                <td bgcolor='#555555' width=300 align=left>Say [Some] to Jark Kaladim(in the Mine).  He talks about how lazy his wife is and how she failed to bring him his dinner and asks that you do so. Telling him [I will get your dinner] will spawn Nella (near the Cleric Guild). Hail her and say [dinner] and she will mention that she forgot about his dinner and asks that you bring it to him. Hand in the dinner to Jark.</td>
              </tr>

